50|$|Jiang is of Korean {{descent and}} {{was born on}} Feb 8th, 1932, in Longjing, in Yanbian Korean Autonomous Prefecture, Jilin Province, China. He became the first Chinese {{scientist}} in researching <b>microwave</b> <b>remote</b> <b>sensing</b> technology after he participated {{in the creation of}} China's first space satellite, Dong Fang Hong I. He is the founder of China's National <b>Microwave</b> <b>Remote</b> <b>Sensing</b> Laboratory (NMRS), Chinese Academy of Science.|$|E
