40|$|A {{textbook}} prepared {{primarily for}} use in introductory courses in <b>remote</b> <b>sensing</b> is presented. Topics covered include concepts and foundations of remote sensing; elements of photographic systems; introduction to airphoto interpretation; airphoto interpretation for terrain evaluation; photogrammetry; radiometric characteristics of aerial photographs; aerial thermography; multispectral scanning and spectral pattern recognition; <b>microwave</b> sensing; and <b>remote</b> <b>sensing</b> from space...|$|R
